name: NorthstarMLS
listing_address: CONCAT_WS(' ',   nullif(StreetNumber,''),   nullif(StreetDirPrefix,''),  nullif(StreetName,''),  nullif(StreetSuffix,''),  nullif(StreetDirSuffix,''),  nullif(UnitNumber,''))
listing_price: IF(  CASE WHEN (AuctionType IS NOT NULL AND AuctionType <> 'N/A') THEN 0 WHEN PropertyType='Residential Rental' THEN ListPrice WHEN standardstatus IN ('Closed') THEN ClosePrice ELSE coalesce(ListPrice,0) END > 99999999,  NULL,  CASE WHEN (AuctionType IS NOT NULL AND AuctionType <> 'N/A') THEN 0 WHEN PropertyType='Residential Rental' THEN ListPrice WHEN standardstatus IN ('Closed') THEN ClosePrice ELSE coalesce(ListPrice,0) END)
listing_foreclosure: IF(SpecialListingConditions LIKE '%Foreclosure%' OR SpecialListingConditions LIKE '%Short Sale%' OR SpecialListingConditions LIKE '%Real Estate Owned%' ,1,0)
listing_style: case   when PropertyType = 'Multi-Family' then case PropertySubTypeAdditional                                               when 'Duplex Side by Side' then '(MF) Duplex Side X Side'                                               when 'Apartments/Multi Family' then '(MF) Apartments'                                               else CONCAT('(MF) ', COALESCE(PropertySubTypeAdditional, 'Other')) end   else case PropertySubType            when '(TH) Side by Side' then '(TH) Side x Side'            when 'Apartment         ' then '(RT) Apartment'            when '(RT) Duplex Side by Side' then '(RT) Duplex Side x Side'            when '(RT) Four Plex' then '(RT) Fourplex'            when 'Time Share        ' then 'Time Share'            when 'Duplex Side by Side' then '(MF) Duplex Side X Side'            when 'Apartments/Multi Family' then '(MF) Apartments'            else PropertySubType end end
listing_num_photos: CASE WHEN StandardStatus = 'Closed' AND PictureDownloadedCount > 0 THEN 1 ELSE PictureDownloadedCount END

name: Northwest MLS
listing_address: trim(concat(case when streetnumber is not null && streetnumber !=0 then concat(streetnumber, ' ') else '' end, case when streetnumbermodifier is not null and streetnumbermodifier <> '' then concat(streetnumbermodifier, ' ') else '' end, case when streetdirection is not null and streetdirection  <> '' then concat(streetdirection, ' ') else '' end, case when streetname is not null and streetname <> '' then concat(streetname, ' ') else '' end, case when streetsuffix is not null and streetsuffix <> '' then concat(streetsuffix, ' ') else '' end, case when streetpostdirection is not null and streetpostdirection  <> '' then concat(streetpostdirection, ' ') else '' end, case when unit is not null and unit <> '' then concat ('#', unit, ' ') else '' end))
listing_state:
CASE
WHEN StateOrProvince LIKE 'Wa%' THEN 'WA'
WHEN StateOrProvince LIKE 'Or%' THEN 'OR'
ELSE StateOrProvince
END
listing_price: coalesce(case when sellingprice between 1 and 2147483646 then sellingprice else null end, listingprice)
listing_num_baths: CASE WHEN (COALESCE(BathsFullTotal, 0) + COALESCE(BathsHalfTotal, 0) + COALESCE(BathsThreeQuarterTotal, 0)) > 0 THEN (COALESCE(BathsFullTotal, 0) + COALESCE(BathsHalfTotal, 0) + COALESCE(BathsThreeQuarterTotal, 0)) else BathroomCount end
listing_num_baths_total: CASE WHEN (COALESCE(BathsFullTotal, 0) + COALESCE(BathsHalfTotal, 0) + COALESCE(BathsThreeQuarterTotal, 0)) > 0 THEN (COALESCE(BathsFullTotal, 0) + COALESCE(BathsHalfTotal, 0) + COALESCE(BathsThreeQuarterTotal, 0)) else BathroomCount end
listing_foreclosure: CASE WHEN ThirdPartyApprovalRequired LIKE '%short sale%' THEN 1 WHEN BankOrRealEstateOwned = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END
listing_num_photos: IF(status in ('Active', 'Contingent') OR status like 'pending%', PictureDownloadedCount, least(PictureDownloadedCount, 1))
listing_off_market_date: case when StatusDate > NOW() then MatrixModifiedDT else StatusDate end
listing_sales_close_date: case when status='Rented' then MatrixModifiedDT else SellingDate end
openhouse_from_datetime: cast(concat(left(FromDate,10),' ',case when FromTime < 600 then floor(FromTime / 100) + 12 when FromTime >= 2400 then null else floor(FromTime / 100) end,':',FromTime % 100,':00') as datetime)
openhouse_to_datetime: cast(concat(left(FromDate,10),' ',case when ToTime < 800 then floor(ToTime / 100) + 12 when ToTime >= 2400 then null else floor(ToTime / 100) end,':',ToTime % 100,':00') as datetime)
openhouse_type: CASE WHEN OpenhouseType like 'Public%' then 'Public' else 'Broker' END
openhouse_virtual_description: if(virtualopenhouseurl IS NOT NULL, Description, NULL)
agent_is_member_for_count_criteria: OfficeID IN (SELECT OfficeID FROM nwmls_offices WHERE OfficeID NOT IN (3972,4567) AND (OfficeType IS NULL OR OfficeType IN ('Appraisal Office', 'Associate/Title/Escrow', 'Broker Office', 'Not Applicable', 'NON Member', 'Olympic Office', 'State Wide Forms', 'Trial Membership', 'Win Member Office'))) and MUC IN ('AI - Agent W\\ Input', 'ANI - Agent W\\ No Input', 'AP - Appraiser', 'AS - Assistant', 'ASI - Assistant W\\ Input', 'BI - Broker W\\ Input', 'BNI - Broker W\\ NoInput', 'CI - Clerical W\\Input', 'CNI - Clerical W\\NoInput') and MemberStatus IN ('Active','Suspended') and MemberType NOT IN ('NON MEMBER', 'Olympic MLS Broker ', 'Olympic MLS Sales Agent ', 'SA DELETED/W-KEY', 'Olympic Clerical ', 'Associate', 'Auth Signer/Charge', 'Whatcom Key holder', 'Other', 'Olympic Appraiser', 'Other', 'Trial Branch Broker ', 'Trial Des Bro', 'Trial Sales Agent', 'Trial Clerical', 'WIN Agreements', 'Jefferson Xpress Forms Users ', 'NWMLS STAFF', 'Quasi Governmental Agency', 'Governmental user')
agent_roster_criteria: nwmls_agents.OfficeID IN (SELECT OfficeID FROM nwmls_offices WHERE OfficeID NOT IN (3972,4567) AND (OfficeType IS NULL OR OfficeType IN ('Appraisal Office', 'Associate/Title/Escrow', 'Broker Office', 'Not Applicable', 'NON Member', 'Olympic Office', 'State Wide Forms', 'Trial Membership', 'Win Member Office'))) and MUC IN ('AI - Agent W\\ Input', 'ANI - Agent W\\ No Input', 'AP - Appraiser', 'AS - Assistant', 'ASI - Assistant W\\ Input', 'BI - Broker W\\ Input', 'BNI - Broker W\\ NoInput', 'CI - Clerical W\\Input', 'CNI - Clerical W\\NoInput') and MemberStatus IN ('Active','Suspended') and MemberType NOT IN ('NON MEMBER', 'Olympic MLS Broker ', 'Olympic MLS Sales Agent ', 'SA DELETED/W-KEY', 'Olympic Clerical ', 'Associate', 'Auth Signer/Charge', 'Whatcom Key holder', 'Other', 'Olympic Appraiser', 'Other', 'Trial Branch Broker ', 'Trial Des Bro', 'Trial Sales Agent', 'Trial Clerical', 'WIN Agreements', 'Jefferson Xpress Forms Users ', 'NWMLS STAFF', 'Quasi Governmental Agency', 'Governmental user')
agent_cell_phone:
CASE
  WHEN ContactPhoneType = 'Cellular' THEN ContactPhone
  ELSE NULL
END
attachments_type: CASE WHEN Type = 'Portable Document Format' THEN 'pdf' ELSE NULL END
agent_photo_url: CASE WHEN HasPicture = 1 THEN CONCAT('https://mobilerealtyapps-agent-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/14/l/',nwmls_agents.matrix_unique_id,'.jpg') ELSE NULL END
listing_is_rental: case when propertytype='Single Family' and PropertySubType in ('Rental')  then 1 end

listing_num_baths:
CASE
  WHEN COALESCE(CAST(total_baths AS UNSIGNED), COALESCE(num_full_baths_total,0) + COALESCE(num_full_baths_total,0)) <> 0
  THEN COALESCE(CAST(total_baths AS UNSIGNED), COALESCE(num_full_baths_total,0) + COALESCE(num_full_baths_total,0))
  ELSE (COALESCE(u1_half_baths + u1_full_baths,0) + COALESCE(u2_half_baths + u2_full_baths,0) + COALESCE(u3_half_baths + u3_full_baths,0) + COALESCE(u4_half_baths + u4_full_baths,0))
END
listing_num_baths_total:
CASE
  WHEN COALESCE(CAST(total_baths AS UNSIGNED), COALESCE(num_full_baths_total,0) + COALESCE(num_full_baths_total,0)) <> 0
  THEN COALESCE(CAST(total_baths AS UNSIGNED), COALESCE(num_full_baths_total,0) + COALESCE(num_full_baths_total,0))
  ELSE (COALESCE(u1_half_baths + u1_full_baths,0) + COALESCE(u2_half_baths + u2_full_baths,0) + COALESCE(u3_half_baths + u3_full_baths,0) + COALESCE(u4_half_baths + u4_full_baths,0))
END
listing_square_feet:
CASE
  WHEN coalesce(finished_sqft, total_finished_sqft) IS NOT NULL 
  THEN coalesce(finished_sqft, total_finished_sqft) 
  ELSE NULLIF(COALESCE(u1_sqft,0) + COALESCE(u2_sqft,0) + COALESCE(u3_sqft,0) + COALESCE(u4_sqft,0), 0) 
END

name: Zillow Interchange Format
listing_agent_id_1:
CASE
WHEN zif_listings.customer_id = 1294 THEN concat(Agent_EmailAddress, ":", office_brokeragename) ##Real Estate One
ELSE Agent_EmailAddress											
END
listing_address: trim(case when Location_StreetAddress like concat('%', Location_UnitNumber) then Location_StreetAddress else concat_ws(' ',Location_StreetAddress,if(length(Location_UnitNumber)>0,concat('#',Location_UnitNumber),'')) end)
listing_price:
IF(ListingDetails_Status='Sold',
   COALESCE(ListingDetails_PriceSold,IF(ListingDetails_Price > 99999999, NULL, ListingDetails_Price)),
   IF(ListingDetails_Price > 99999999, NULL, ListingDetails_Price))
listing_num_baths: if(BasicDetails_Bathrooms>=0 and BasicDetails_Bathrooms regexp '^[0-9.]+$',BasicDetails_Bathrooms,coalesce(BasicDetails_FullBathrooms,0) + coalesce(BasicDetails_HalfBathrooms,0) + coalesce(BasicDetails_QuarterBathrooms,0) + coalesce(BasicDetails_ThreeQuarterBathrooms,0))
listing_date:
CASE WHEN ListingDetails_Status='sold' THEN 
       case when ListingDetails_DateSold regexp '^[0-9]{1,2}/[0-9]{1,2}/[0-9]{4}($|T| )' 
	          then str_to_date(ListingDetails_DateSold, '%c/%d/%Y') 
            when ListingDetails_DateSold regexp '^[0-9]{4}-[0-9]{1,2}-[0-9]{1,2}($|T| )' 
			  then str_to_date(ListingDetails_DateSold, '%Y-%c-%d') 
            end 
	 else 
	   coalesce(
		 case when ListingDetails_DateListed regexp '^[0-9]{1,2}/[0-9]{1,2}/[0-9]{4}($|T| )' 
	          then str_to_date(ListingDetails_DateListed, '%c/%d/%Y') 
            when ListingDetails_DateListed regexp '^[0-9]{4}-[0-9]{1,2}-[0-9]{1,2}($|T| )' 
			  then str_to_date(ListingDetails_DateListed, '%Y-%c-%d') 
            end 
		,zif_listings.added_timestamp) 
	 end
listing_sales_close_date:
case when ListingDetails_DateSold regexp '^[0-9]{1,2}/[0-9]{1,2}/[0-9]{4}($|T| )' then str_to_date(ListingDetails_DateSold, '%c/%d/%Y') 
     when ListingDetails_DateSold regexp '^[0-9]{4}-[0-9]{1,2}-[0-9]{1,2}($|T| )' then str_to_date(ListingDetails_DateSold, '%Y-%c-%d') 
end

   WHEN num_of_bathrooms LIKE '%.%' THEN TRUNCATE(num_of_bathrooms, 0) + 1
   WHEN num_of_bathrooms LIKE '%+%' THEN REPLACE(num_of_bathrooms,'+','')

END

CASE
   WHEN num_of_bathrooms = 'Zero' THEN 0
   WHEN num_of_bathrooms LIKE '%.%' THEN TRUNCATE(num_of_bathrooms, 0) + 1
   WHEN num_of_bathrooms LIKE '%+%' THEN REPLACE(num_of_bathrooms,'+','')

END
listing_num_baths_full:
CASE
   WHEN num_of_bathrooms = 'Zero' THEN 0
   WHEN num_of_bathrooms LIKE '%.%' THEN TRUNCATE(num_of_bathrooms, 0)
   WHEN num_of_bathrooms LIKE '%+%' THEN REPLACE(num_of_bathrooms,'+','')
   ELSE num_of_bathrooms
END

END
